description._content: Original Collection: Harriet's Collection Item Number: HC0596 Image Description: Corvallis City Hall located on 4th and Madison (southeast corner) before the Fire Station addition. It was built in 1892 and demolished in the 1950s You can find this image by searching for the item number by clicking here. Want more? You can find more digital resources online.
